  - sinnerName: John CDGV
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c645ab7c1d05ffe4e88f05f67ea863c1, type: 3}
    sinnerDialogue: Heed my words. I am John. Traitor of CDGV. And I have never known
      defeat
